snippet.title: umineko op
snippet.description: This is the opening video from the visual novel Umineko no naku koro ni episode 1 Legend of the golden witch. I downloaded the game a few days ago and I think it's awesome. I do not claim ownership over Umineko no naku koro ni or this video, they both belong to there copyright owner Ryukishi 7 or seventh expansion. If you want to play all of the episodes I would go to the witch hunt site and look around, I'll give you the link : http://witch-hunt.com/. And also if you cant figure out how to play all of the episodes you can check out the umineko manga its still continuing and will be for some time, heres the link : http://www.mangareader.net/557/umineko-no-naku-koro-ni.html.
